item.title: OSCP Endgame – Inside the dark world of the inner self
item.description: Brief overview Fear, disappointment, failure with many other bad things have been experienced by most of OSCP holders, It’s not a shame to admit it and if you ask people around regarding its difficulty, you will get various types of answers with one signification. OSCP is the toughest exam they’ve taken in their lives. Offensive Security Certified Professional. one of the most well-recognized and respected certifications in the security industry.
